domain.interfaces
Interface ReactedAction

All Superinterfaces:
Action
public interface ReactedAction
extends Action

This is a subinterface of Action. It represents an Action instance wich it's execution will be the consequence of a Collision or other event kind. A ReactedAction is an Action wich will be executed as a consequence of another event kind (A Collision, for example).
